---
const paragraphs = [
  'Dear Colleague,',
  'You are receiving this because your work has, in some measurable way, changed how veterinarians think and practise. That is not a common achievement, and it is not one I take lightly in extending this invitation.',
  'Veterinary Academy International was founded on a simple observation: exceptional clinical educators are rarely given the structure, time, or production support to teach at the level their expertise deserves. Continuing education is too often fragmented, hastily produced, and disconnected from the realities of clinical practice. We are building something different.',
  'Founding Faculty are not contributors to a course library. They are the people who will define what postgraduate veterinary education looks like when it is done properly, with the same rigour and care that they bring to their own clinical work. Every part of the process, from educational design to filming to long-term stewardship of the material, is built around protecting your time and your standards.',
  'What follows on this page is an honest account of what that collaboration involves. I would ask you to read it as you would a colleague’s case notes: carefully, and with your own judgement intact.',
  'I look forward to the conversation.',
];
---
<section class="bg-ivory">
  <div class="container-prose py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl">
      <div class="eyebrow mb-8">From the Founder</div>
      <div class="prose-editorial font-serif text-navy-deep">
        {paragraphs.map((p) => (
          <p class="text-xl md:text-[1.375rem] leading-[1.7] mb-7">{p}</p>
        ))}
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 md:mt-14 flex items-center gap-7">
        <div class="h-[130px] w-[130px] md:h-[150px] md:w-[150px] shrink-0 overflow-hidden rounded-full bg-platinum-soft">
          <img
            src="/founder-portrait.png"
            alt="Dr. Soheyl Simaei"
            class="h-full w-full object-cover"
            style="object-position: 50% 20%;"
            loading="lazy"
            decoding="async"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-serif text-2xl text-navy-deep">Dr. Soheyl Simaei</div>
          <div class="text-sm tracking-[0.02em] text-muted mt-1.5">Founder</div>
          <div class="text-sm tracking-[0.02em] text-muted">Veterinary Academy International</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
